Title: Tuskarr Fishing Gear
Description:
Hi again, $n.

<Rowie looks around and hums a little tune.>

Oh right! Tavio was making me a new net and said she could make you one too. She can make some other fishing gear too if you bring her all the stuff.

You should go talk to her.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Tavio at Iskaara in The Azure Span.
RewardText: My family is known as the best weavers of nets and crafters of harpoons. If you bring me the supplies I need, I can craft some new tools for you.
